name: SoteMix
description:
Merged the anime models I use the most. Credit goes to the original model authors.

Positive Prompts:
(masterpiece, best quality, highres)
Negative Prompts:
(worst quality, low quality:1.4, lowres), (monochrome, zombie)

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras
Steps: 30
Highres: Latent with 0.6 denoise and 20 steps.
Or R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B with 0.5 denoise for Anime style.
Clip Skip: 2



Mege:
0.7(0.75(0.75(0.75(0.75(0.75(0.5(SomethingV2_2) + 0.5(meinapastel_v5Anime)) + 0.25(meinaalter_v2)) + 0.25(meinamix_meinaV9)) + 0.25(nyanMix_230303Intense)) + 0.25(mixProV4_v4)) + 0.25(breakdomain_M2150)) + 0.3(0.4(SomethingV2_2) + 0.6(meinapastel_v5Anime))

And baked in Blessed2 VAE
